channel.title: Just a simple design for a rsps website. Give some feedback if you want
channel.description:
I was bored so I made a simple design for a rsps website. I didn't spend alot of time in this because I have alot of work to do for school etc... This is just the design but when I have enough time I will code it and upload the template.
Give some feedback if you want. I know that the footer needs to be better but I will fix that later.
[IMG]http://i59.tinypic.com/207kdpl.jpg[/img]
